        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Question:- Design a circular shaft transmitted 90 kW at 180 rpm. the maximum torque is exceeding the mean by 40%. take shear stress is 70 MPa, length of shaft 2m. and modulus of rigidity 90 GPa. Also find the angle of twist."
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Solution:"
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "Power = 90 \\text{ kW} = 90 \\times 10^3 \\text{ W}",
          "display": true
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "N = 180 \\text{ rpm}",
          "display": true
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "\\omega = \\frac{2\\pi N}{60}",
          "display": true
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "P = \\frac{2\\pi N T_{mean}}{60} \\implies T_{mean} = \\frac{60P}{2\\pi N}",
          "display": true
        }
